  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488620/extras/11b56c5f9ef46664be5d49e323daaf07.avif?t=1748912330\" width=610 height=396 /></span><br><br>Be One of the 20 with EA SPORTS™ F1® 24, the official video game of the 2024 FIA Formula One World Championship™. Unleash your champion in pursuit of a legacy-defining F1® Career, the mode’s first major update since 2016. Drive like the greatest and feel at one with the car through the all-new EA SPORTS Dynamic Handling System. Ignite your passion by connecting to your favorite teams and drivers while proving that you have what it takes across new modes and experiences.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488620/extras/5a2bc347144b8b89b86658f197aa009c.avif?t=1748912330\" width=610 height=3030 /></span><br><br>This game includes optional in-game purchases of virtual currency that can be used to acquire virtual in-game items.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488620/extras/11b56c5f9ef46664be5d49e323daaf07.avif?t=1748912330\" width=610 height=396 /></span><br><br>Be One of the 20 with EA SPORTS™ F1® 24, the official video game of the 2024 FIA Formula One World Championship™. Unleash your champion in pursuit of a legacy-defining F1® Career, the mode’s first major update since 2016. Drive like the greatest and feel at one with the car through the all-new EA SPORTS Dynamic Handling System. Ignite your passion by connecting to your favorite teams and drivers while proving that you have what it takes across new modes and experiences.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488620/extras/5a2bc347144b8b89b86658f197aa009c.avif?t=1748912330\" width=610 height=3030 /></span><br><br>This game includes optional in-game purchases of virtual currency that can be used to acquire virtual in-game items.",
